snippet.title: SNK HEROINES Tag Team Frenzy - Love Heart, Reporting for Duty! (Switch, PS4)
snippet.description:
Learn more @ https://SNKHeroines.com
Preorder @ https://store.nisamerica.com/preorders/snk-heroines

From Sky Pirate to Dream Police Officer, it's Love Heart, reporting for duty!

Who will be the belle of the brawl? SNK's toughest female fighters are pitted against one another in a brand-new 2 vs 2 fighting game! With a streamlined control system and unique KO mechanic, this is a fighting game built for fans of all levels of experience. The perfect dream match starts here! Coming to Nintendo Switch and PlayStation 4 in Summer 2018!
